data.description: Come see this charming Waldo Ranch. This well-lit two-bedroom, one bath home showcases a host of recent upgrades, including a stunning new bathroom, refinished hardwood floors, a freshly painted interior, newer roof, upgraded plumbing and a huge backyard. This home boosts with comfort and style, offering a unique blend of classic charm and contemporary convenience.  The seller is willing to sell the home furnished.
